lead_paragraph: Detroit infield prospect JaCoby Jones hit a tiebreaking three-run homer in the seventh inning and the Tigers beat Florida Southern 7-2 on Monday for their 11th straight victory over the Moccasins.

headline.print_headline: Tigers Prospect Jones Homers in 7-2 Win Over Fla Southern
